#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:2
msgid "Assignment 1"
msgstr "Zadatak 1"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:4
msgid ""
"Open your existing map project and revise it thoroughly. If you have noticed"
" small errors or things you'd have liked to fix earlier, do so now."
msgstr ""
"Otvorite svoj postojeći projekat karte i temeljno ga revidirajte. Ako ste "
"primetili sitne greške ili stvari koje ste ranije želeli da popravite, "
"uradite to sada."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:7
msgid ""
"While customizing your map, keep asking yourself questions. Is this map easy"
" to read and understand for someone who's unfamiliar with the data? If I saw"
" this map on the Internet, or on a poster, or in a magazine, would it "
"capture my attention? Would I want to read this map if it wasn't mine?"
msgstr ""
"Dok prilagođavate svoju kartu, stalno se pitajte. Da li je ova karta laka za"
" čitanje i razumevanje nekome ko nije upoznat sa podacima? Da li bih, ako "
"bih video ovu kartu na internetu, ili na posteru, ili u časopisu, obratio "
"pažnju na nju? Da li bih želeo da pročitam ovu kartu da nije moja?"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:12
msgid ""
"If you're doing this course at a ``★☆☆`` Basic or ``★★☆`` Intermediate "
"level, read up on techniques from the more advanced sections. If you see "
"something you'd like to do in your map, why not try to implement it?"
msgstr ""
"Ako pohađate ovaj kurs na ``★☆☆`` osnovnom ili ``★★☆`` srednjem nivou, "
"pročitajte o tehnikama iz naprednijih odeljaka. Ako vidite nešto što biste "
"želeli da uradite na svojoj karti, zašto ne biste pokušali da to primenite?"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:16
msgid ""
"If this course is being presented to you, the course presenter may require "
"you to submit a final version of your map, exported to PDF, for evaluation. "
"If you're doing this course by yourself, it's recommended that you evaluate "
"your own map using the same criteria. Your map will be evaluated on the "
"overall appearance and symbology of the map itself, as well as the "
"appearance and layout of the map page and elements.  Remember that the "
"emphasis for evaluating the appearance of maps will always be *ease of use*."
" The nicer the map is to look at and the easier it is to understand at a "
"glance, the better."
msgstr ""
"Ako vam se ovaj kurs izlaže, predavač kursa može zahtevati da predate "
"konačnu verziju svoje karte, izvezenu u PDF, radi ocenjivanja. Ako ovaj kurs"
" radite sami, preporučuje se da ocenite sopstvenu kartu koristeći iste "
"kriterijume. Vaša karta biće ocenjena po ukupnom izgledu i simbologiji same "
"karte, kao i po izgledu i rasporedu strane karte i elemenata. Zapamtite da "
"će naglasak pri ocenjivanju izgleda karata uvek biti *lakoća korišćenja*. "
"Što je karta lepša za gledanje i što je lakše razumljiva na prvi pogled, to "
"bolje."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:25
msgid "Happy customizing!"
msgstr "Srećno prilagođavanje!"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:28
msgid "In Conclusion"
msgstr "Zaključak"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/map_composer/day_1_assignment.rst:30
msgid ""
"The first four modules have taught you how to create and style a vector map."
" In the next four modules, you'll learn how to use QGIS for a complete GIS "
"analysis. This will include creating and editing vector data; analyzing "
"vector data; using and analyzing raster data; and using GIS to solve a "
"problem from start to finish, using both raster and vector data sources."
msgstr ""
"Prva četiri modula su vas naučila kako da napravite i stilizujete vektorsku "
"kartu. U naredna četiri modula naučićete kako da koristite QGIS za potpunu "
"GIS analizu. Ovo će uključivati pravljenje i uređivanje vektorskih podataka;"
" analizu vektorskih podataka; korišćenje i analizu rasterskih podataka; i "
"korišćenje GIS-a za rešavanje problema od početka do kraja, koristeći i "
"rasterske i vektorske izvore podataka."
